rss.channel:
The Valve Wire Weekly
https://thevalvewire.com
A weekly podcast covering the latest in transcatheter valve technology — TAVR, mitral repair and replacement, tricuspid therapies, clinical trials, and industry analysis. Balanced, evidence-based analysis with expert skepticism. Hosted by E. Nolan Beckett.
