E. Nolan Beckett
Weekly analysis of transcatheter valve technology developments for cardiac surgeons, interventional cardiologists, trainees, patients, and industry stakeholders. We present balanced, circumspect analysis — always questioning whether therapies have gotten ahead of the evidence.

  E. Nolan Beckett
